edu.ucsb.cs56.games.client_server.v2.client.Views

Class OnlineViewPanel

  • java.lang.Object
    • GameViewPanel
      • edu.ucsb.cs56.games.client_server.v2.client.Views.OnlineViewPanel

  • public class OnlineViewPanel
extends GameViewPanel
    The lobby panel is a panel which displays currently available games which, when clicked on, will take the user to a new or in-progress copy of that game. Soon, buttons will take players to instruction screens where they can choose a few settings and specify if they want any server, or specifically an empty one to start a new game
    Version:
    for CS56, Spring 2013
    Author:
    Joseph Colicchio, Adam Ehrlich
